OL,7,FA Barnstaple man who attacked
OL,8,Fvulnerable residents in a care home he
OL,9,Fbroke into has been jailed for ten
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FExeter Crown Court heard how Drew
OL,13,FDavey carried out the "senseless and
OL,14,Fbrutal" attack in the early hours of
OL,15,F16 August last year.
OL,17,FHe had been drinking and arguing with
OL,18,Fhis girlfriend before entering the
OL,19,Fsheltered housing in Lulworth,
OL,20,FWestward Ho!
