OL,7,FDavey then fell asleep in a shed in
OL,8,Fthe garden of the care home but was
OL,9,Fwoken by two residents who had gone
OL,10,Foutside to smoke.
OL,12,FHe reacted by launching the attack,
OL,13,Fwhich ended in the kitchen.
OL,15,FTwo of the victims, who were
OL,16,Fvulnerable care home patients, were
OL,17,Frepeatedly hit over the head with a
OL,18,Fbroom handle, the court heard.
