OL,7,FDavey was then disturbed again by a
OL,8,Fstaff member who had gone to
OL,9,Finvestigate the noise. Davey hit the
OL,10,Fmember of staff in the face.
OL,12,FDespite being injured, the third
OL,13,Fvictim managed to alert police to the
OL,14,Fincident.
OL,16,FDevon and Cornwall Police said the
OL,17,Fresidents were discovered with
OL,18,Fsignificant head wounds and taken to
OL,19,Fhospital in a serious condition, where
OL,20,Fthey remained for a number of weeks.
