OL,7,FThey were also left with life-changing
OL,8,Fbleeds on the brain after being hit
OL,9,Frepeatedly.
OL,11,FDavey was found hiding in a bush in a
OL,12,Fgarden close to the scene and arrested.
OL,14,FDefending, Anna Vigars KC, said Davey
OL,15,Fwas struggling with mental health
OL,16,Fissues at the time of the attack.
