OL,7,FShe said that he had no memory of the
OL,8,Fattack and was horrified when police
OL,9,Ftold him what had happened, adding
OL,10,Fthat he is extremely remorseful for
OL,11,Fhis actions.
OL,13,FIn court, onlookers in the public
OL,14,Fgallery at Exeter Crown Court were
OL,15,Fwarned to look away as gruesome
OL,16,Ffootage from a police body cam showed
OL,17,Fthe kitchen with both men lying in
OL,18,Fpools of their own blood.
