OL,7,FDavey admitted two counts of causing
OL,8,Fgrievous bodily harm with intent and
OL,9,Fone of causing actual bodily harm and
OL,10,Fwas jailed for ten years with a three
OL,11,Fyear extended licence by Judge Stephen
OL,12,FClimie.
OL,14,FHe classified him as a dangerous
OL,15,Foffender and told him: "The two
OL,16,Fvictims were in mid-life and had
OL,17,Fsuffered historically so far as their
OL,18,Fhealth was concerned. They were highly
OL,19,Fvulnerable and in a care home.
