OL,7,FAfter the case, Deputy Senior
OL,8,FInvestigating officer DS John Crewe
OL,9,Fsaid: "My team and I welcome today's
OL,10,Fsentence. Mr Davey subjected three
OL,11,Fcompletely innocent members of the
OL,12,Fpublic to a horrific, senseless, and
OL,13,Fbrutal attack.
