OL,7,F"Two of these men were already
OL,8,Fextremely vulnerable and it was luck
OL,9,Fmore than judgement that these two men
OL,10,Fin particular didn't lose their lives.
OL,11,FThey were left with severe injuries
OL,12,Fleaving them both in hospital for a
OL,13,Fnumber of weeks thereafter and with a
OL,14,Fcatalogue of ongoing complications.
OL,16,F"I hope this sentence affords these
OL,17,Fmen and their families a sense of
OL,18,Fjustice of which they can try to
OL,19,Frebuild their lives.
